guy berkeley " berke " breathed ( ; born june 21 , 1957 ) is an american cartoonist , children 's book author/illustrator , director and screenwriter , best known for bloom county , a 1980s cartoon - comic strip that dealt with sociopolitical issues as understood by fanciful characters ( e.g. , bill the cat and opus the penguin ) and through humorous analogies .

comic strips : on december 8 , 1980 berkeley breathed began his magnum opus with the debut of this strip

